  "description": "This individual is a lean, middle-aged human with taupe skin and brown eyes set beneath heavy lids that give the face a perpetually appraising cast. Brown hair is worn in a precise parted style, exposing a high forehead and the fine lines of long indoor work. The mouth is narrow and straight, and the jaw shows the mild asymmetry of an old, well-healed knock. Their hands are notably broad-fingered and callused at the tips, a permanent mark of constant handling of seals, cords, and paper.",
